# PolyForm Noncommercial License 1.0.0

## Acceptance
In order to receive this license, you must agree to its rules. The rules of this license are both conditions of your agreement and conditions to your license. You do not have to accept this license or agree to its rules, but but if you do not, you do not have any license to use the software.

## Copyright and Patent
Each contributor licenses you to do everything with the software that would otherwise infringe that contributor's copyright or patents, for any noncommercial purpose.

## Noncommercial Purpose
A noncommercial purpose is one that is not primarily intended for or directed towards commercial advantage or monetary compensation. For example, use by an individual for personal enjoyment or by an educational institution for classroom teaching is a noncommercial purpose. Use by a corporation or other business for its internal business purposes is not a noncommercial purpose.

## Distribution
Each contributor also licenses you to distribute the software, provided that you include the full text of this license and all of its notices with every copy you distribute.

## Notices
You must ensure that any copyright or other proprietary notices that the contributors have included in the software are reproduced in every copy of the software that you distribute.

## No Other Rights
This license does not grant you any other rights, such as rights to any contributor's trademarks or service marks.

## Termination
If you violate any of the rules of this license, your license to use the software terminates immediately.

## No Warranty
The software is provided "as is", without any warranty of any kind. Each contributor excludes all liability for any damages you may suffer from your use of the software.

## Patent Defense
If you bring a patent claim against any contributor for anything that contributor has done with the software, your license to use the software terminates immediately.
